CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Department of Natural Resources – Commercial Invasive Blue and Flathead
3 Catfish Finfish Trotline License Pilot Program – Alterations
4 FOR the purpose of altering the commercial blue and flathead catfish finfish trotline license
5 to allow a person to catch blue catfish with certain gear Invasive Blue Catfish Pilot
6 Program to include the Blue Catfish Gill Net Program; and generally relating to the
7 commercial blue and flathead catfish finfish trotline license Invasive Blue Catfish
8 Pilot Program.
9 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
10 Article – Natural Resources Chapter 171 of the Acts of the General Assembly of 2025
11 Section 4–701.2
12 Annotated Code of Maryland
13 (2023 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
14 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
15 Chapter 172 of the Acts of the General Assembly of 2025
16 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
17 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
18 Chapter 171 of the Acts of 2025
EXPLANATION: CAPITALS INDICATE MATTER ADDED TO EXISTING LAW.
[Brackets] indicate matter deleted from existing law.
